question: Show all science fiction books and romance books published in 2018.
sql_query1:
SELECT Books.title 
FROM Books
WHERE (Books.Book_Genre = "Science Fiction Book" OR Books.Book_Genre = "Romance Book") AND Books.Year_Of_Publication = 2018
sql_query2:
SELECT Books.title 
FROM Books
WHERE Books.Book_Genre = "Science Fiction Book" OR Books.Book_Genre = "Romance Book" AND Books.Year_Of_Publication = 2018
interpretation1: Show all books in the science fiction published in 2018 or romance genres, which were published at the same time.
interpretation2: Show all science fiction books regardless of publishing date, also show the romance books published in 2018.
